A Hotel Management Software
1. LogIn
  1.1 create unique log in
  1.2 verify log in
  1.3 recover username/password
2. Availabilities/Booking
  2.1 input desired beds and date of stay
  2.2 display availabilites
  2.3 room selection / secure checkout 
3. Auto-Messaging
  3.1 billing confirmation
  3.2 pre-check in auto message (contains code to room)
  3.3 forward messages to staff
4. Key Code/Code Generator
  4.1 generate unique code for room upon arrival 
  4.2 invalidate code for room after check out (prevents security breach)
5. Maintenence/Room Service
  5.1 routes phone call to staff cell phones through phone management system
  5.2 allow the staff to contact the guest.
